Response ID: resp_1937
Response Text: I'd like them to have more prescence via both links to more info and applications and with hard copy available to those who do not have access to computers or cellphones. You might be surprised
how many artists are challenged by those elements! Information and education are key elements to any successful venture...
Also, i appreciate very much what the city has done to insure living wages to creatives through it's own programs, but it seems important for our citizens as well as any venue that is looking to rent or to hire to fully understand the time commitment, experience, education and talent (this means rehearsals!) creatives require to build a career or even just produce one show. If cultural funding programs or some part of ACME could address outreach to help with that understanding, i think it would help us create a better, more supportive community for the arts.

